Comment: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還真是寬敞啊
Comment: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看起來是有好好打掃過了
Comment: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還不錯呢
