Comment: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,處決!
Comment: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是的  我是今天開始在這裡住宿的...
