Comment: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還請多多指教 三鷹前輩
Comment: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前輩就不必了
Comment: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,叫我仁就好了
Comment: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個 仁 可不可以麻煩你幫個忙呢?
