Comment: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之先喝杯水冷靜冷靜吧
Comment: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯?
Comment: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個時間是?
Comment: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,老師? 還是仁? 回來了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妖...妖...妖怪怪怪怪...
Comment: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隔壁的房間啊...
Comment: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是活生生的...
Comment: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類吧?
Comment: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在吵什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊! 鬼怪出現了啊...
Comment: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想在這裡終結你的人生嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,老師啊
Comment: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聯誼回來了?
Comment: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,早就回來了
Comment: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是的 各個都是一堆低等貨
